lass=\"textFootnotes\">\n    \n      <p class=\"std\"><span class=\"textMark\">a<\/span>This is not a verbatim statement, but report in the minutes of the meeting of the\n        conference held on that day.<\/p>\n    \n    \n      <p class=\"std\"><span class=\"textMark\">b<\/span>This is also a statement from the minutes of the Prophet&rsquo;s remarks as recorded by\n        the scribe, not a verbatim report but a synopsis.<\/p>\n    \n    \n      <p class=\"std\"><span class=\"textMark\">c<\/span>Shortly after the organization of the Church the Lord commanded Joseph Smith to make\n        a translation of the Bible by revelation. It had been made known in the translation of the Book of Mormon that\n        because of iniquity &ldquo;many plain and precious things&rdquo; were &ldquo;taken away from the book, which<\/p>\n    \n  <\/div>\n<\/div>"}